{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1706-08_163"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Divers couplets de chansons]","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", août 1706 [tome 8], p. 163-173.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#"}}},{"p":{"value":"Rien n’étant plus agréable que la varieté, je passe à une matiere bien differente, en vous envoyans divers couplets de Chanson. Le premier a paru du temps d’Henry IV. &amp; même sous le nom de ce Monarque ; le voicy.","id":"/div/#[2]/p"}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Charmante Gabrielle,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}},"note":{"@resp":"author","@place":"margin","#1":{"value":"L’Air qui commence par, ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/note/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Charmante Gabrielle","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/note/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":", page 163.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/note/#2"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Percé de mille dards ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand la Gloire m’appelle","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À la suite de Mars :","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cruelle départie !","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Malheureux jour !","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ne suis-je sans vie,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou sans amour !","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}}},{"p":{"value":"Cette Chanson estant devenuë tellement à la mode, qu’on la chante tous les jours dans les plus belles compagnies, Mr Charles a jugé à propos de faire un Air nouveau, sur les mêmes paroles ; j’ay fait graver l’ancien au dessus du nouveau, &amp; je vous les envoye tous deux. Je vous envoye aussi plusieurs couplets qui peuvent estre chantez sur ces deux Airs, &amp; dont les premiers doivent avoir servi de suite aux couplets precedens.","id":"/div/#[4]/p"}},{"quote":{"#":[{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Bel astre, je vous quitte,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O ! cruel souvenir !","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ma douleur s’en irrite,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous revoir ou mourir.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cruelle départie, &amp;c.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[0]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[1]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Recevez ma Couronne,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le prix de ma valeur.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je la tiens de Bellonne ;","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tenez-la de mon cœur.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O sort digne d’envie !","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trop heureux jour !","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est trop peu d’une vie","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour tant d’amour.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je n’ay pû dans la guerre","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’un Royaume gagner ;","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais sur toute la terre","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vos yeux doivent regner.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O sort digne d’envie, &amp;c.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/#[2]/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}},{"p":{"value":"Vous jugez bien que le couplet qui suit regarde Monsieur de Vendosme.","id":"/div/#[6]/p"}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Fils de Gabrielle","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Arrive dans ces lieux ;","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une gloire immortelle","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le rend égal aux Dieux :","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les cœurs sur son passage,","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vont aujourd’huy :","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que veut-il davantage ?","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils sont à luy.","id":"/div/#[7]/quote/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}}},{"p":{"value":"Le couplet que vous allez lire ne regarde plus ce Prince.","id":"/div/#[8]/p"}},{"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On n’a que trop à craindre","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Auprés de vos beaux yeux :","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais bien loin de m’en plaindre,","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je veux mourir pour eux.","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O sort digne d’envie !","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trop heureux jour !","id":"/div/#[9]/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"h